com.amazon.device.associates
Class Product

java.lang.Object
  com.amazon.device.associates.Product
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable

Represents a physical product in Amazon Catalog. The product is represented by Product ID, Product Title, Product Description, Product Price and Product Image URL. You can retrieve product data by using ShoppingService.search(SearchRequest) or ShoppingService.searchById(SearchByIdRequest). Make sure you clearly communicate product information to the user when presenting an offer for a physical product.
